{{redirect|Bel Paese|the type of cheese|Bel Paese (cheese)}}
{{Wiktionary|bel paese}}
'''''Bel paese''''' (or '''''Belpaese''''', {{IPA-it|ˌbɛl paˈeːze; -eːse|IPA}}) is the classical poetical appellative for [[Italy]], meaning the "beautiful country" in [[Italian language|Italian]], due to its mild weather, cultural heritage and natural endowment.

The usage of the term originated in the [[Middle Ages]], being used by [[Dante Alighieri|Dante]] and [[Petrarch]]:

{{quote
| text = del '''bel paese''' là dove 'l sì suona,
| sign = [[Dante Alighieri|Dante]]
| source = ''[[Divine Comedy]]'': [[Inferno (Dante)|Inferno]], [[:s:it:Divina Commedia/Inferno/Canto XXXIII|canto XXXIII, line 80]]
}}

{{quote
| text = Of the fair land there where the 'Sì' doth sound,
| sign = [[Dante Alighieri|Dante]]
| source = ''[[Divine Comedy]]'': [[Inferno (Dante)|Inferno]], [[:s:The Divine Comedy/Inferno/Canto XXXIII|translated by Henry Wadsworth Longfellow]]
}}

{{quote
| text = <poem>il '''bel paese'''
ch'Appennin parte e 'l mar circonda e l'Alpe</poem>
| sign = [[Petrarch]]
| source = ''[[Canzoniere]]'', [[:s:it:Canzoniere (Rerum vulgarium fragmenta)/O d'ardente vertute ornata et calda|CXLVI, lines 13-14]]
}}

{{quote
| text = <poem>that fair country
the Apennines divide, and Alps and sea surround</poem>
| sign = [[Petrarch]]
| source = ''[[Canzoniere]]'', [http://petrarch.petersadlon.com/canzoniere.html?poem=146, translation by A.S. Kline]
}}

The term is currently widely used in modern Italian as in other languages as a synonym for Italy, but can sometimes be intended slightly [[irony|ironically]].<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CE855BighvAC&lpg=PA231&ots=-4wCus6nzs&dq=Italy%3A%20Farewell%20to%20the%20'Bel%20Paese&pg=PA231#v=onepage&q=&f=false |title=Italy: Farewell to the 'Bel Paese'? |publisher=Berg Publishers |year=1999 |accessdate=2009-11-30}}</ref> It is commonly used as a term of endearment by members of the [[Italian diaspora]], and it is often used to endorse or promote goods<ref>[[Bel Paese (cheese)]]</ref> and services<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.google.com/search?q=&quot;bel+paese&quot;+restaurant | title=Google results for '"Bel Paese" restaurant' |accessdate=2009-11-30}}</ref> both in Italy and abroad.

