{{Infobox company | name = Botswana Savings Bank | logo = | type = [[State owned company]] | industry = [[Banking]] | founded = {{start date |1992}} | hq_location_city = [[Gaborone]] | hq_location_country = [[Botswana]] | key_people = | products = | owner = Government of Botswana | num_employees = | num_employees_year = | parent = | website = {{URL |http://www.bsb.bw/}} }}
'''Botswana Savings Bank''' '''BSB''', is a financial services organization in [[Botswana]]. It is licensed as a [[International financial institutions|development bank]] by the [[Bank of Botswana]], the national banking regulator.<ref>[http://www.bankofbotswana.bw/assets/uploaded/2010-directory-of-financial-institutions-alphabetical.pdf Directory of Financial Institutions Licensed In Botswana]</ref>
==Overview== BSB is a government-owned financial services organisation that mobilizes domestic savings by accepting customer deposits, grants loans on commercial terms and offers other financial services as it considers necessary to meet the needs of the people of [[Botswana]]. Established in 1992 by act of parliament, the bank offers savings accounts, mortgage loans, automobile loans and other secured loans to its customers. The Bank is a member of the [[World Savings Banks Institute]].<ref>[http://www.bsb.bw/html/products.htm Financial Services Offered By Botswana Savings Bank] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100831023721/http://www.bsb.bw/html/products.htm |date=August 31, 2010 }}</ref> According to the [[Bank of Botswana]], Botswana Savings Bank had an asset base of approximately US$73 million (BWP:480 million) as of December 2009.<ref>[http://www.bankofbotswana.bw/assets/uploaded/2010-directory-of-financial-institutions-alphabetical.pdf#Botswana_Savings_Bank Botswana Savings Bank December 2009 Total Assets]</ref>
==Branches== The bank maintains two (2) branches; one in [[Gaborone]] and another in [[Francistown]]. In addition, BSB has a partnership agreement with [[BotswanaPost]] to offer banking services through over 120 postal outlets throughout the country.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.botspost.co.bw/|title=Botswana Post {{!}} We deliver, whenever whaterver|website=www.botspost.co.bw|access-date=2017-08-16}}</ref>
