==External links== * [http://www.south-pole.com/p0000099.htm Douglas Mawson 1882–1958] * [https://web.archive.org/web/20050911022520/http://geonames.usgs.gov/stategaz/ANTARCTICA.TXT All features of Antarctica listed in one single *.TXT-File, provided by the United States Geological Survey (USGS)] In this document, BANZARE appears often, a search for "BANZARE" shows which features BANZARE was involved with.
