{{Infobox newspaper | name = Le Phare de Majunga | logo = | image = Le phare de majunga 9 November 1931 issue.png | caption = November 8, 1931 issue of ''Le Phare de Majunga'' | type = Weekly | format = | owners = | founder = | publisher = | editor = | chiefeditor = | assoceditor = | maneditor = | newseditor = | managingeditordesign = | campuseditor = | campuschief = | opeditor = | sportseditor = | photoeditor = | seniorstaff = | staff = | foundation = 1908 | political = | language = [[French language]] | ceased publication = | relaunched = | headquarters = [[Majunga]] | circulation = | sister newspapers = | ISSN = | oclc = | website = }} '''''Le Phare de Majunga''''' was a [[French language]] weekly newspaper published from [[Majunga]], [[Madagascar]].<ref name="p2">''[https://books.google.com/books?id=IlnQAAAAMAAJ Nomenclature des journaux & revues en langue française du monde entier]''. Paris, Les bureaux de l'Argus, 1937. p. 474</ref> The newspaper was founded in 1908.<ref name="p2"/>
