{{Infobox settlement <!-- Basic info ---------------->| name = Sheikh Hasina Cantonment | settlement_type = Cantonment <!-- images and maps ----------->| image_skyline = | image_caption = | image_flag = | image_seal = | image_map = | map_caption = | subdivision_type = Country | subdivision_name = {{Flag|Bangladesh}} | subdivision_type1 = Division | subdivision_type2 = District | subdivision_name1 = [[Barisal]] | subdivision_name2 = [[Patuakhali]] | established_title = Established | established_date = | parts_type = | parts_style = | parts = <!-- Politics -----------------> | government_footnotes = | government_type = | leader_title = | leader_name = | leader_title1 = | leader_name1 = | area_footnotes = | area_magnitude = | area_total_km2 = 6.1997 | area_total_sq_mi = <!-- Elevation --------------------------> | elevation_footnotes = | elevation_m = | elevation_ft = <!-- Population -----------------------> | population_total = <!-- General information ---------------> | population_as_of = | population_footnotes = | population_note = | postal_code_type = | postal_code = | area_code = | website = | footnotes = | timezone1 = [[Bangladesh Standard Time|BST]] | utc_offset1 = +6 | timezone_DST = | utc_offset_DST = | latd = | latm = | lats = | latNS = | longd = | longm = | longs = | longEW = }}
'''Sheikh Hasina Cantonment''' is a proposed [[cantonment]] and headquarter of [[7th Infantry Division (Bangladesh)|7th Infantry Division]] of [[Bangladesh Army]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ispr.gov.bd/%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%80%E0%A7%9F-%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%A7%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%80-%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%B0-6/|title=মাননীয় প্রধানমন্ত্রী কর্তৃক লেবুখালীতে শেখ হাসিনা সেনানিবাস উদ্বোধন এবং সদর দপ্তর ৭ পদাতিক ডিভিশনসহ ১১টি সদর দপ্তর/ইউনিটের পতাকা উত্তোলন - ISPR|website=www.ispr.gov.bd|language=en-US|access-date=2018-02-17}}</ref> It is located in Lebukhali, Patuakhali. The area of the cantonment is 1532 acres. The project will be completed by the [[Ministry of Defence (Bangladesh)|Ministry of Defence]] by June 2021.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/2017/11/14/ecnec-approves-tk-1699cr-sheikh-hasina-cantonment-project/|title=Ecnec approves Tk 1,699cr Sheikh Hasina Cantonment project {{!}} Dhaka Tribune|website=www.dhakatribune.com|language=en-US|access-date=2017-11-26}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/backpage/new-cantonment-patuakhali-1491349|title=New cantonment in Patuakhali|date=2017-11-15|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2017-11-26|language=en}}</ref>
== History == The "Sheikh Hasina Cantonment" will be established as part of the governments long-term modernization scheme for [[Bangladesh Armed Forces]] called the "[[Forces Goal 2030]]".
[[Prime Minister of Bangladesh|Prime Minister]] [[Sheikh Hasina]] green lighted the project in 2014.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bdnews24.com/bangladesh/2017/11/13/bangladesh-building-sheikh-hasina-cantonment-to-add-coastal-areas-to-national-defence-system|title=Bangladesh building 'Sheikh Hasina Cantonment' to add coastal areas to national defence system - bdnews24.com|date=2017-11-26|access-date=2017-11-26|deadurl=bot: unknown|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171126114414/https://bdnews24.com/bangladesh/2017/11/13/bangladesh-building-sheikh-hasina-cantonment-to-add-coastal-areas-to-national-defence-system|archivedate=2017-11-26|df=}}</ref> She first announced it during a winter exercise of Bangladesh Armed Forces in January 16, 2015.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/govt-to-set-up-two-more-cantonments-60184|title=Govt to set up two more cantonments|date=2015-01-16|work=The Daily Star|access-date=2017-11-26|language=en}}</ref>
The Executive Committee of the National Economic Council approved the project ‘Establishment of Sheikh Hasina Cantonment, Barisal’ on November 14, 2017. The set up of this cantonment will cost approximately Tk 1,699 crore.<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />
On February 8, 2018 Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina inaugurated the cantonment.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/nation/2018/02/08/pm-reaches-patuakhali/|title=PM inaugurates Sheikh Hasina Cantonment in Patuakhali {{!}} Dhaka Tribune|website=www.dhakatribune.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-02-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dhakatribune.com/bangladesh/nation/2018/02/07/hasina-to-visit-patuakhali-barisal/|title=PM Hasina to visit Patuakhali, Barisal Thursday {{!}} Dhaka Tribune|website=www.dhakatribune.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-02-08}}</ref>
